    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z-Force recon is a single player horror game. You're hired to work for a military company and tasked to complete 4 missions. There are weird creatures which are roaming around causing issues. Your task is to successfully complete these missions and escape unscathed. Are you up for the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/de162439bc539ef4bcd0634a5b838b00.avif?t=1732601604\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras_big/de162439bc539ef4bcd0634a5b838b00.avif?t=1732601604 width=800 height=266 /></span>Background: <br>So you accepted the military contract and decided to take on the challenge? Welcome! You are now an employee of the military tasked with a secret mission. Your goal is to complete all the tasks you've been given while solving multiple puzzles to finish these missions succesfully. Don't forget, you also have to deal with the creatures creeping around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Choose from 4 unique mission and their locations</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/344d8504f830bfdc7b3348c59d88b8b0.poster.avif?t=1732601604\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/344d8504f830bfdc7b3348c59d88b8b0.webm?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/344d8504f830bfdc7b3348c59d88b8b0.mp4?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple different puzzles</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/9e8df8633e37883fb1e70da0e441c796.poster.avif?t=1732601604\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/9e8df8633e37883fb1e70da0e441c796.webm?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/9e8df8633e37883fb1e70da0e441c796.mp4?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different creatures you need to fight</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/7e37a3194baec8729c0290a57305602c.poster.avif?t=1732601604\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/7e37a3194baec8729c0290a57305602c.webm?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316840/extras/7e37a3194baec8729c0290a57305602c.mp4?t=1732601604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
